    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! \ud83d\udc4b You have seriously got to check out this absolute beauty! It\u2019s in such pristine shape that you\u2019d honestly think it just rolled off the showroom floor yesterday. I\u2019ve absolutely babied this car\u2014the interior is spotless, the paint is glowing, and it drives like a total dream. If you\u2019re looking for that 'brand new' feeling without the brand new price tag, this is the one! Come take it for a spin and fall in love! \u2728",
      "price": 44500.0,
