    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Presenting a truly exceptional, showroom-quality vehicle that satisfies even the most discerning collector. This car has been meticulously preserved in a climate-controlled environment, and its condition is indistinguishable from the day it left the factory. The exterior features a flawless, deep-gloss finish with no swirl marks, rock chips, or imperfections, further protected by a professional-grade ceramic coating. Inside, the cabin remains in pristine state; the premium leather upholstery is supple with zero bolster wear, the carpets are spotless, and it retains that distinct new-car aroma. Mechanically, this vehicle is beyond reproach. It has been serviced exclusively by master technicians using OEM parts, with a comprehensive folder of service records included to document its pampered history. Every electronic feature, from the high-fidelity sound system to the advanced driver assists, functions perfectly. This is a rare opportunity to own a 'time capsule' example that offers a new-car experience at a pre-owned value. Sold with two sets of keys, the original window sticker, and a clean title in hand.",
      "price": 46500.0,
