      "description": "Offered is an investment-grade E46 M3 in concours-level condition. This specimen features the high-revving S54B32 power plant, utilizing individual throttle bodies and double VANOS variable valve timing to deliver a linear power band up to its 8,000 RPM redline. The chassis remains structurally impeccable, featuring proactive subframe reinforcement and a recent rod bearing service using VAC coated bearings. Power is managed via a crisp 6-speed Getrag manual gearbox and a factory limited-slip differential. Suspension geometry remains factory-spec with fresh bushings and Bilstein dampers, ensuring the quintessential M-division handling profile. Zero oxidation, original paint depth, and a pristine interior make this a definitive collector\u2019s example.",
